<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.3.3">
<l>kāṭuka ḷūṭupōyk kaṉṟukaḷ mēyttu maṟiyōṭi kārkkō ṭalpūc</l>
<l>cūṭi varukiṉṟa tāmō tarākaṟṟut tūḷikā ṇuṉṉu ṭampu</l>
<l>pēṭai mayiṟcāyal piṉṉai maṇāḷā nīrāṭṭa maittu vaittēṉ</l>
<l>āṭi yamutuce yappaṉu muṇṭila ṉuṉṉō ṭuṭaṉē yuṇpāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Dāmodara who comes adorned with dark lily blossoms,</l>
<l rend="indent">Having gone to the forest, grazing and herding the claves!</l>
<l>Look [at you]! Your body [covered] in dust from the calves.</l>
<l>Bridegroom of Piṉṉai with the likeness of a pea-hen!</l>
<l>I have prepared [your] bath. [Come] take [your] bath and eat!</l>
<l>[Your] father has not eaten [yet]; he will eat with you.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
